      "title": "Akila to a higher position",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "United National Party Vice Leader Mr. Akila Viraj Kariyawasam has been appointed to the position of Senior Advisor to the President.",
        "Mr. Akila Viraj Kariyawasam has been appointed as the President's Senior Advisor on Administrative Affairs.",
        "The appointment was made by President Ranil Wickramasinghe."
